saṃvidā saṃvedanena yady aśeṣollekhaparihārāt tat tattvaṃ pratyakṣam anubhūtaṃ syāt | etac caivaṃvidhaṃ satyadvayātmakam ubhayāntarahitaṃ śūnyatākaruṇābhinnaṃ prajñopāyasvarūpaṃ sadgurupādaprasādavitter jñeyam ||

<commentary>tad eva sopaskāram āha—yāvān ityādi | yatas tatra madhyamārthe yāvān samāropo 'dhyavasāyaḥ sa sarvo nāsti | evaṃvidhaḥ samāropābhāvo vijñānanaye apīṣṭaḥ | ata āha—sarvatheti | tatra hi vijñānasya vastusattvasamāropāspadatvam asti | ato na tatra sarvathā samāropābhāvaḥ |

etena māyopamasiddhānto 'pi pratyuktaḥ | kutaḥ | āstāṃ tāvad atra sarvavikalpo 'dhyavasāyānām apohaviṣayatayā nirāropatvaṃ ca vijñānavāde 'pi nirāropasambhavāt | tato madhyamārtho nirāropo niṣprapañcaḥ | param ayaṃ viśeṣaḥ | vijñānavāde nirvikalpatve 'pi gāḍhataravijñānasadbhāvāvidyāvaśād āhatyollekhābhāve 'pi cetasi tadaiva svasaṃvidgrahāt pṛṣṭhe vedanagrahaḥ sphuṭa eva | 

nanu tavāpy etat samam | pṛṣṭhe sarvavikalpabhāvāt | na | apratiṣṭhānatvenānāstheyasattvānurodhāt saṃvṛtyā vyavahārāt | atas tatrāpohavidhī vidhiniṣedhau kutaḥ | naivety arthaḥ |</commentary>

tarhi pratīyamānā bhāvāḥ kathaṃ jñeyāḥ | ata āha—jñānetyādi | tatra hi jñānajñeyasamāropaśūnye tattvātmake jagati manyatā savikalpanirvikalpābhyāṃ nānyathā |
